body:
Thoughts On Super Mario Party

- Phil saying they should put a pipe on the screen so it looks like Dan popped up from it, ugh his mind!

- Dan sounds so happy that he won two Dan vs Phil’s, what a cute bean!

- 0:44 Dan looking at the pong one is very funny!

- 0:55 Phil….. you seriously tried to PRINT out WHITE PAPER oh Phil this is the funniest thing ever

- 1:04 Dan looks at the camera giving the “this guy” look and I agree 100%

- 1:32 Dan’s giggles, adorable!

- I love that Dan vs Phil is just silence and a noise now

- 2:30 Dan doing that cute little lonely impression, why do I feel like he’s done this before

- 2:39 Dan goes “ooh!” And it made me soft for an unknown reason

- Monty Mole is what Phil looks like in the morning

- 1:55 “thats me….. a mask with nothing behind it” Dan shut up with that edgy bullshit

- 3:07 I thought Phil was joking when he said that

- 3:15 Dan says Phil looks like Walugi and obviously he’s joking but the way he says it😂

- 3:19 “and I look the most like Rosalina” Dan just wanted to make himself a princess didn’t he?

- But saying Phil looks like the bad guy and Dan looks like the princess….. what is he saying haha

- 3:28 “I want it very hard” DAN WTF

- 3:35 they judge because all the girls are in normal, we love feminist kings! (Or princess for Dan)

- 4:15 Dan judging Phil for keeping on going after it said to and calling him grandad is very soft

- “lead us dad” this is the first time Phil has ever said something like that and it feels not right

- I love that they quit when they realize how long it is

- 5:20 Phil is talking to Dan like he’s stupid when Dan asks if Peach is the only human is the content I needed

- 5:27 “I’ll knaw your neck off, I am a mole” this has a whole new meaning when you remember that Dan is very sensitive in his neck…..

- 5:42 Dan saying he finds it really cool that Phil’s a mole, well Dan you find everything Phil does cool and amazing and heroic

- 6:00 “Phil’s copying me look at this guy” Second “this guy” of the video

- 6:35 “That was SPORT” Yes Dan I’m sure it took a lot of your athletic abilities to tilt your control forward

- 6:47 Dan gets soft and tells everyone to be safe, my heart is beating for this boy

- 7:29 Dan’s cute and confused little “really?” When he realizes he’s doing it wrong is adorable!

- 7:40 Phil teasing Dan for messing up his words, so cute they’re both so teasy today

- 8:10 Dan is so sad that he lost and starts whining aw and Phil teased him and gets all up close haha

- 8:32 Dan is once again confused and adorable, he’s so soft and cute

- 8:50 Dan is very whiny in this video but I’m not complaining, whiny Dan is adorable

- 9:40 Dan’s little “are you joking?” At the motion controls, aw baby!

- 9:50 Dan right here is just so precious with his little movements and smiling and giggling!

- 10:15 Phil’s “I was” sounds so fond in contrast to Dan’s whining makes my heart pure and soft

- 10:24 Phil immediately saying “there’s one more” to make his whiny baby happy again, Phil is whipped AF

- 10:28 PHIL FUCK OFF THE LOVE EYES AND FOND CHUCKLE ARE TOO MUCH

- 10:32 “what if I want to get tackled” Well Dan than you can let Phil tackle you later

- 10:40 I love this story Phil gives from his childhood although the game doesn’t sound fun haha

- 11:35 Dan’s “oh dear” I love that Dan says that so much

- 12:21 Dan’s heart eyes when Phil put it on his forehead aW

- 12:59 that whole build up speech just to say he wants to do All or Nothing, oh Dan

- 13:00 Phil agrees to do, like I said before, whipped AF

- 13:20 “Phil goes with the one with popcorn, I’m not surprised” but you are in love seriously what kind of boyfriend bullshit is that sentence

- 13:49 “that’s what I want to see before I die” really? I think popcorn is overrated, I know, I’m not valid

- 14:25 Dan whining when he lost and Phil teasing him is too much for my poor, demon heart

- 14:45 I love that Dan actually gives it to Rosalina

- 14:40, 14:43, and 14:44 Phil is the most fond looking boyfriend ever and I’m about to go full demon

- 15:15 Dan teasing Phil, this video is a lot

This video is SO cute!
